name: Elon's Galaxy Crusher
description: My Submission for #HENthousand, all will be remaining copies will be burned.  The Galaxy Crusher: A sword thought to be lost to the Galaxy when Elon the Great and Doge the Fluff took one final stand in the void of space to vanquish Lord Bitcoin and his high pollutin’ ways. Elon’s space x roadster 420 was shot down during the battle over Uranus and they were never seen again. This artifact was recovered by his best mate President Joe Rogan, who vowed to avenge his beloved friends in a fury of blood, steel, jujitsu, and DMT.
